  <brief_title>Adjuvanted Influenza Vaccine Effectiveness in the Elderly (65+Yrs)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Case-Control Study to Evaluate the Effectiveness of Adjuvanted Trivalent Inactivated Influenza Vaccine in the Elderly Aged ≥65 Years.</official_title>
