  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study explores the hypothesis that the use of an adjuvanted influenza vaccine in the
      elderly will produce greater vaccine effectiveness in their group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the effectiveness of adjuvanted trivalent inactivated influenza vaccine in the
      elderly (aged ≥ 65 years) through the reduction in relative risk of microbiologically
      confirmed influenza illness
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
